def module hloguys
def desc "Hit once with axe, then automatically switch to mace and perform stun slam"

on left_click if playing {
    if holding #axe {
       switch #mace 
       wait 0.05 {
         input left
       }
    }
}

If you actually wanted to use the sword instead of mace just switch it to #sword